# Extension build-time defaults (Vite).
#
# --- Public (safe to commit) ---
# Root `.env.production` is tracked in git with the production API URL.
# `VITE_COVERCLICK_API_ORIGIN` is NOT a secret — it is baked into the extension
# bundle and used for sign-in, billing, and API calls.
#
# Production (committed in `.env.production`, no trailing slash):
#   VITE_COVERCLICK_API_ORIGIN=https://coverclick-production.up.railway.app
#
# --- Local overrides (gitignored — use `.env` or `.env.local`) ---
# Local API testing (with `npm run server:dev` on port 8787):
#   VITE_COVERCLICK_API_ORIGIN=http://localhost:8787
#
# Optional: force mock generation in dev builds (skips Google / Stripe gate for UI-only dev)
# VITE_USE_MOCK=true
